{"tid":1521801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"輕鐵多左好多cam","createTime":"2019-08-31T10:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T07:48:47.000Z","uid":9838,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"284a7bc5dc2e17aa01cd3495ee6377bd030a920e","tid":1521801,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:51:47.000Z","msg":"車內除左之前車頭司機位後面果個影全車之外，而家每隻門都有一隻，車尾又有一隻<br />\n最過份車外車尾都有一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0fef2030d23489ffd52688275fc4f6184d14f3","tid":1521801,"uid":139282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:53:05.000Z","msg":"［化學］如何清洗顏色水劑（含acrylics/PMMA）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. hot sodium carbonate solution</span><br />\n<br />\n-蘇打水，溫度50度或更高，建議自己開，落多小小都唔怕<br />\n（同小蘇打sodium bicarbonate有啲分別，唔知bicarbonate效果係點）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.消毒火酒（酒精）/含消毒火酒成份濕紙巾</span><br />\n<br />\n3<span style=\"color: red;\">.化妝水</span>/卸妝水/洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n可以洗到有acrylics/PMMA嘅顏料<br />\n<br />\n紅字係考慮完availability, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢</span><br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal"},{"pid":"00525b2650edb19ac297dbc5639a3b2215631203","tid":1521801,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35758c7e856b3eff78591e998933085a5595176","tid":1521801,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:15:52.000Z","msg":"地區的兒子需要<span style=\"color: red;\">接送 睇水</span><br />\n<br />\n要拖鞋換 小心螢光鞋底路<br />\n<br />\nGASTBY 冰紙巾好似抹到"},{"pid":"785d10c571a3a62f303cd3533607b33f66615b19","tid":1521801,"uid":137309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:16:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"95e3a3bb1bb55a71a1cb0adc896a4d363d264af5","tid":1521801,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:16:38.000Z","msg":"輕鐵站已經大把CCTV"},{"pid":"c1a564acaccbb9ca2721374c29e932b71bb55a2a","tid":1521801,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:18:35.000Z","msg":"噴"},{"pid":"15a206b2c97b0ed638dc76bac36590bb89b7fae6","tid":1521801,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a35758c7e856b3eff78591e998933085a5595176","tid":1521801,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:15:52.000Z","msg":"地區的兒子需要<span style=\"color: red;\">接送 睇水</span><br />\n<br />\n要拖鞋換 小心螢光鞋底路<br />\n<br />\nGASTBY 冰紙巾好似抹到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:18:59.000Z","msg":"街坊 幫 睇下邊d 出口安全"},{"pid":"a7e28f84a306209b72af5309c64c66f6bf08d7df","tid":1521801,"uid":314979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:19:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2qFcjPk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2qFcjPk.gif&h=3ec89b83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1feb9624b4d61c07a96d24537b48e49a822d3ad8","tid":1521801,"uid":143945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95e3a3bb1bb55a71a1cb0adc896a4d363d264af5","tid":1521801,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:16:38.000Z","msg":"輕鐵站已經大把CCTV"},"citedBy":0,"re